<br />No, but you can finish any achievement in Animal Crossing: Wild World (other than the tutorial mission) twice as fast with two DS systems and two Game Cards. Or (obNESdev) you can split audio, CPU, PPU pixel rendering, and PPU filtering into separate threads in an NES emulator.

		

